OL,3,CChris Kaba: Officers on trial after
OL,4,Cshooting suspects to have anonymity
OL,6,FThis comes after Martyn Blake's
OL,7,Fanonymity was lifted before the trial
OL,8,Fbegan, raising concerns about his
OL,9,Fsafety, as Sam Holder reports
OL,11,FPolice officers who shoot suspects
OL,12,Fwill be anonymous during criminal
OL,13,Ftrials, the home secretary has
OL,14,Fannounced in the wake of the Chris
OL,15,FKaba case.
OL,17,FYvette Cooper told the House of
OL,18,FCommons there would be a "presumption
OL,19,Fof anonymity for firearms officers
OL,20,Fsubject to criminal trial... up to the
OL,21,Fpoint of conviction".
