OL,3,CChris Kaba: Officers on trial after
OL,4,Cshooting suspects to have anonymity
OL,6,F"When officers act in the most
OL,7,Fdangerous situations on behalf of the
OL,8,Fstate it is vital that those officers
OL,9,Fand their families are not put in
OL,10,Ffurther danger during any subsequent
OL,11,Flegal proceedings," she told MPs.
OL,13,FThe announcement from the home
OL,14,Fsecretary came after Sergeant Martyn
OL,15,FBlake was cleared of murder this week
OL,16,Ffollowing the death of Chris Kaba in
OL,17,FLambeth in 2022.
OL,19,FBlake's anonymity was lifted before
OL,20,Fthe trial began, raising concerns
OL,21,Fabout his safety.
