OL,3,CChris Kaba: Officers on trial after
OL,4,Cshooting suspects to have anonymity
OL,6,FCooper said it was crucial that
OL,7,F"Sergeant Blake and his family are
OL,8,Fgiven the time and space that they
OL,9,Fwill need to recover from what will
OL,10,Fhave been an immensely difficult
OL,11,Fexperience for them".
OL,13,F"For an armed police officer to be
OL,14,Fprosecuted for actions taken in the
OL,15,Fcourse of their duties is very rare so
OL,16,Fof course this case has raised
OL,17,Fconsiderable concerns for the public
OL,18,Fand the police."
