OL,3,CChris Kaba: Officers on trial after
OL,4,Cshooting suspects to have anonymity
OL,6,FShadow Home Secretary James Cleverly
OL,7,Fwelcomed most of the announcements,
OL,8,Fbut warned "we have seen too often
OL,9,Fpolice leadership bend to
OL,10,Finappropriate levels of public
OL,11,Fpressure", urging MPs to be
OL,12,F"thoughtful and careful" when making
OL,13,Fcomments on social media about cases
OL,14,Flike that of Chris Kaba.
OL,16,FThe prime minister told reporters on
OL,17,FTuesday night: "It is important that
OL,18,Fthe public have confidence in the
OL,19,Fpolice including of course the armed
OL,20,Fpolice."
