OL,3,CChris Kaba: Officers on trial after
OL,4,Cshooting suspects to have anonymity
OL,6,FMr Kaba, who was 24, was unarmed when
OL,7,FMr Blake shot him through the
OL,8,Fwindscreen of an Audi Q8 as he tried
OL,9,Fto ram his way past police cars on
OL,10,FSeptember 5 2022.
OL,12,FIt was revealed this week he was a
OL,13,F"core member" of one of London's most
OL,14,Fdangerous criminal gangs and was
OL,15,Fallegedly directly linked to two
OL,16,Fshootings in the six days before he
OL,17,Fwas shot dead by police, a court has
OL,18,Frevealed to the public after lifting
OL,19,Freporting restrictions.
